race.comment: CUMBRIA BENNY (4) was strongly fancied on the back of a win two starts back but finished third last time (29.72) at Wentworth Park. Form from his last run is proving strong. Top prospect. KUNG FU BAY (8) is in hot form after clocking a handy 20.68 victory two back then followed up with a 21.09 win at this track over 365m last time. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent form. MISSION TO FLY (2) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (21.21) in a Grade 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Well placed here and can atone this time. QUEEN CHARLM (3) is right in the mix.
